Class UserDTO

  • java.lang.Object
    • mph.beans.dto.UserDTO

    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ProfessorDTO, StudentDTO

    public abstract class UserDTO
extends java.lang.Object
implements EntityDTO
    This abstract class will be extended by the DTO's containing the information about a user.
    It implements the EntityDTO interface.
